{"title":"twitter","uid":"d93b5039256bd1807f9e545758741a1c","slug":"hexo-tag-twitter","date":"2022-12-26T16:16:00.842Z","updated":"2022-12-22T18:41:21.918Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/hexo-tag-twitter.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<script src=\"/test/assets/asciinema-player.js\"></script><link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" href=\"/test/assets/asciinema-player.css\" /># hexo-tag-twitter\n\n<p>Embed Twitter tweet tag plugin for <a href=\"https://github.com/hexojs/hexo\">Hexo</a>.</p>\n<h2 id=\"Introduction\"><a href=\"#Introduction\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Introduction\"></a>Introduction</h2><p>This is a Hexo tag plugin which allows you to embed Twitter tweet on your blog posts.</p>\n<h2 id=\"DEMO\"><a href=\"#DEMO\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"DEMO\"></a>DEMO</h2><p><a href=\"https://photo-tea.com/p/hexo-tag-twitter/\">https://photo-tea.com/p/hexo-tag-twitter/</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"Installation\"><a href=\"#Installation\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Installation\"></a>Installation</h2><figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm install hexo-tag-twitter --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h2 id=\"Usage\"><a href=\"#Usage\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Usage\"></a>Usage</h2><figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&#123;% twitter tweet-url %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>or</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&#123;% twitter tweet-id user-id %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>If you use <code>tweet-id</code> only , please edit your <code>_config.yml</code></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">tagTwitter:</span><br><span class=\"line\">  id: tea0828</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h2 id=\"FAQ\"><a href=\"#FAQ\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"FAQ\"></a>FAQ</h2><p>Please read here if you can not display tweet well.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/tea3/hexo-tag-twitter/issues?utf8=%E2%9C%93&q=is:issue+\">hexo-tag-twitter&#x2F;issues&#x2F;</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"Example\"><a href=\"#Example\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Example\"></a>Example</h2><p>For example, if you want embed <a href=\"https://twitter.com/tea0828/status/819885806714138624\">this tweet</a> (This tweet tweet-id is <em>819885806714138624</em>), please enter the following this.</p>\n<h3 id=\"1-When-using-tweet-url\"><a href=\"#1-When-using-tweet-url\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1. When using tweet-url\"></a>1. When using tweet-url</h3><p>Please edit your <code>your-markdown.md</code> . This way is most simple.</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&#123;% twitter https://twitter.com/tea0828/status/819885806714138624 %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h3 id=\"2-When-using-tweet-id-amp-user-id\"><a href=\"#2-When-using-tweet-id-amp-user-id\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2. When using tweet-id &amp; user-id\"></a>2. When using tweet-id &amp; user-id</h3><p>First , please edit your <code>_config.yml</code> .</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">tagTwitter:</span><br><span class=\"line\">  id: tea0828</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>Next , Please edit your <code>your-markdown.md</code> .</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&#123;% twitter 819885806714138624 %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>Also, the above example can coding differently. Please edit your <code>your-markdown.md</code> for this way .</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&#123;% twitter 819885806714138624 tea0828 %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n\n<h2 id=\"License\"><a href=\"#License\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"License\"></a>License</h2><p>MIT</p>\n","text":"# hexo-tag-twitter Embed Twitter tweet tag plugin for Hexo. IntroductionThis is a Hexo tag plugin which allows you to embed Twitter tweet on...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1.2k","symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Introduction\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Introduction</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#DEMO\"><span class=\"toc-text\">DEMO</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Installation\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Installation</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Usage\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Usage</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#FAQ\"><span class=\"toc-text\">FAQ</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Example\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Example</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#1-When-using-tweet-url\"><span class=\"toc-text\">1. When using tweet-url</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-lin